Package com.six.timapi.constants

Enum ResourceId

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<ResourceId>
      • com.six.timapi.constants.ResourceId
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, Comparable<ResourceId>
    public enum ResourceId
extends Enum<ResourceId>

    Enumeration attribute defines which dialog shall be displayed. All dialogs are divided into multiple groups containing dialogs similar operational area.

    Specification: dialog.
